{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-timeline-js","path":"/herrbischoff/awesome-macos-command-line/week/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"awesomeList":{"repo":"herrbischoff/awesome-macos-command-line","descriptionHTML":"<div>Use your macOS terminal shell to do awesome things.</div>","description":"Use your macOS terminal shell to do awesome things."},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2021-06-27T23:07:20.380Z"},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Package Managers</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.finkproject.org\">Fink</a> - The full world of Unix Open Source\nsoftware for Darwin. A little outdated.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Package Managers</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://brew.sh\">Homebrew</a> - The missing package manager for OS X. The most\npopular choice.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Package Managers</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.macports.org\">MacPorts</a> - Compile, install and upgrade either\ncommand-line, X11 or Aqua based open-source software.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>System</h2><h4>Create Bootable Installer</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>For confirmation before erasing the drive, remove <code>–-nointeraction</code> from the\ncommand.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>System</h2><h4>Create Bootable Installer</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>The optional <code>–-downloadassets</code> flag is new in macOS 10.14 (Mojave). It\ndownloads assets which may be required during installation, like updates.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>System</h2><h4>Create Bootable Installer</h4>","itemHTML":"<li>The <code>–-applicationpath</code> flag is deprecated since macOS 10.14 (Mojave) and\nwill throw an error if used.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-09T14:21:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Terminal</h2><h3>A